re will be happy events at home. Good things arising from yourself will occur, so maintain hope and proceed steadily.','August may bring happy events to the family. However, if you mishear others'' words, what seems good at first will turn bad, so judge carefully. Even if your mind is scattered, staying home is best - seek stability.','September is a month when wealth comes through people. Do not neglect relationships; put your heart into meeting people. Fortune is strong - like the moon emerging from clouds to brightly illuminate heaven and earth, your luck brightens.','October may have many problems despite your efforts, but do not be discouraged. A benefactor will appear to help you, and you will ultimately gain wealth. Your steady efforts will be rewarded, so do not give up and keep striving.','November will definitely bring happy events. Following proper order and procedures in matters will yield correct results - proceed step by step and profits will follow. Ignoring conventions may lead to unexpected regret, so be careful.','December sees clouds clearing and the moon emerging as fortune gradually brightens. Stay away from disputes, and if you boast too much, gossip may arise - conduct yourself humbly. If you have worries in your heart, pray in advance to calm your mind, and a bright path will open.','2025-03-02 03:02:00.903186+00','e');

